title: Ep. - 323 - SURVIVING DEATH’S STEPHANIE ARNOLD UNSOLVED MYSTERIES WITH JONATHAN MARK
description:
Stephanie Arnold from Netflix’s Surviving Death, which examines different ways people have experienced the idea that death isn’t the end of life. After the birth of her second child Stephanie suffered a rare—and often fatal—condition called an amniotic fluid embolism (or AFE) and died on the operating table for 37 seconds.

 

Medium Jonathan Mark goes over the unsolved cases of Tara Calico, the Springfield three, D.B. Cooper, Jack the Ripper, and Barbara Beach Hamburg.
